# EasyOCR2

Next-generation ready-to-use OCR with 80+ supported languages and all popular writing scripts.

## Installation

```bash
pip install easyocr2
```

## Quick Start

```python
import easyocr2

# Create reader
reader = easyocr2.Reader(['en'])

# Perform OCR
result = reader.readtext('image.jpg')
print(result)
```

